This challenge teaches you to run a program from a directory. All of the challenges on pwn.college are in a directory called `challenge` and the name of the program is `run`.
So the final path to run the command is `/challenge/run`.
```
Connected!
hacker@paths~program-and-absolute-paths:~$ /challenge/run
Correct!!!
/challenge/run is an absolute path! Here is your flag:
pwn.college{4YaeLloKmzuGcKznlINPBTwXTaN.dVDN1QDL2ETO0czW}
```
